1
00:00:42,080 --> 00:00:43,760
Captains of the Jinwuwei Guards who have come to assist,

2
00:00:44,160 --> 00:00:45,040
and colleagues of the Dali Temple,

3
00:00:45,880 --> 00:00:47,520
recent murders shroud Chang'an like dark clouds.

4
00:00:47,920 --> 00:00:48,600
A gloom that lingers.

5
00:00:49,360 --> 00:00:50,200
Now that night rain is approaching,

6
00:00:50,800 --> 00:00:51,520
I fear another murder may occur.

7
00:00:52,440 --> 00:00:54,880
I, Yao Yuan, ask you to patrol Chang'an tonight.

8
00:00:55,720 --> 00:00:56,720
To ensure the peace of Chang'an.

9
00:00:57,200 --> 00:00:59,160
Vice Minister, just give us your orders.

10
00:01:02,400 --> 00:01:03,480
Of the one hundred and eight Wards in Chang'an,

11
00:01:03,960 --> 00:01:06,080
I entrust the area east of Vermilion Bird Avenue to you.

12
00:01:06,960 --> 00:01:07,280
Yes, sir.

13
00:01:08,200 --> 00:01:08,560
Mu Guiyi.

14
00:01:09,600 --> 00:01:10,800
Lead all personnel of the Dali Temple,

15
00:01:11,400 --> 00:01:12,720
and thoroughly search every Ward along Vermilion Bird Avenue.

16
00:01:13,400 --> 00:01:14,640
Do not miss a single corner.

17
00:01:15,240 --> 00:01:15,480
Yes, sir.

18
00:01:22,360 --> 00:01:23,040
The night rain is coming.

19
00:01:23,360 --> 00:01:24,480
We could not prepare many portraits.

20
00:01:25,040 --> 00:01:26,360
Please memorize this face for now.

21
00:01:27,280 --> 00:01:28,480
Though the murderer's face may differ,

22
00:01:29,000 --> 00:01:30,000
there must be similarities.

23
00:01:30,320 --> 00:01:31,400
If there is even a shred of suspicion,

24
00:01:31,800 --> 00:01:33,040
detain them and bring them to the Dali Temple for questioning.

25
00:01:33,760 --> 00:01:34,360
Yes, sir.

26
00:01:34,680 --> 00:01:35,000
Move out.

27
00:02:12,000 --> 00:02:12,400
You go over there.

28
00:02:12,480 --> 00:02:12,720
Yes, sir.

29
00:02:21,760 --> 00:02:23,240
Have you found anyone suspicious here?

30
00:02:24,240 --> 00:02:24,920
No.

31
00:02:26,360 --> 00:02:27,400
Report immediately if you find anything.

32
00:02:28,440 --> 00:02:28,600
All right.

33
00:02:39,480 --> 00:02:39,720
Let's go.

34
00:02:45,280 --> 00:02:46,440
That darn thief.

35
00:02:47,080 --> 00:02:48,800
Ruining my business so I can't make a living.

36
00:02:59,760 --> 00:03:01,000
Oh, heavens.

37
00:03:01,400 --> 00:03:03,080
If this rain keeps pouring like this,

38
00:03:03,520 --> 00:03:05,360
how am I supposed to survive?

39
00:03:13,800 --> 00:03:15,840
Guest, you must be soaked.

40
00:03:16,320 --> 00:03:17,200
Let me wipe you dry.

41
00:03:19,000 --> 00:03:20,080
My beauty must have faded,

42
00:03:20,280 --> 00:03:21,680
I will go find a younger girl right away,

43
00:03:22,360 --> 00:03:23,520
to clean you up properly, guest.

44
00:03:24,240 --> 00:03:24,400
Guest?

45
00:03:24,720 --> 00:03:25,360
Please, go upstairs.

46
00:03:28,000 --> 00:03:28,600
Slow down, guest.

47
00:03:43,600 --> 00:03:44,520
Your body is already dry.

48
00:03:45,360 --> 00:03:46,360
Guest, please leave quickly.

49
00:03:47,880 --> 00:03:48,480
Why?

50
00:03:49,680 --> 00:03:50,120
No reason.

51
00:03:50,840 --> 00:03:51,400
I just feel unwell.

52
00:03:52,240 --> 00:03:53,240
Forgive me, I cannot serve you.

53
00:03:58,160 --> 00:03:59,560
You lowly whore.

54
00:04:02,400 --> 00:04:04,280
What right do you have to act high and mighty?

55
00:04:05,880 --> 00:04:07,320
Guest, please look at yourself.

56
00:04:07,760 --> 00:04:09,160
What a filthy thing you are.

57
00:04:15,240 --> 00:04:17,560
Let me go! Let me go!

58
00:04:17,760 --> 00:04:19,600
Aren't you meant to be trampled upon by anyone?

59
00:04:19,800 --> 00:04:20,920
Have you no shame?

60
00:04:21,480 --> 00:04:22,920
Someone! Help!

61
00:04:36,320 --> 00:04:38,440
The whores of the world all deserve to die.

62
00:04:40,000 --> 00:04:41,880
All deserve to die! All deserve to die!

63
00:04:59,680 --> 00:05:00,400
You are right.

64
00:05:01,360 --> 00:05:03,200
I am a filthy thing.

65
00:05:04,680 --> 00:05:07,040
The blood of a whore runs in my veins.

66
00:05:09,080 --> 00:05:11,200
I am a filthy thing.

67
00:06:41,360 --> 00:06:42,960
Hong... Hong Ling.

68
00:06:50,240 --> 00:06:52,160
Officers, it is this room.

69
00:07:24,920 --> 00:07:25,520
Is this the person?

70
00:07:28,120 --> 00:07:29,000
Let me wipe you dry.

71
00:07:31,280 --> 00:07:32,240
Somewhat similar.

72
00:07:32,920 --> 00:07:35,520
But the eyes seemed smaller.

73
00:07:36,200 --> 00:07:37,480
The chin seemed pointier.

74
00:07:37,880 --> 00:07:39,640
The nose seemed bigger.

75
00:07:41,280 --> 00:07:42,720
Men, put the deceased down.

76
00:07:43,360 --> 00:07:43,520
Yes, sir.

77
00:07:52,040 --> 00:07:52,840
Every stab wound is fatal, just the same.

78
00:07:55,880 --> 00:07:56,640
And the spleen is missing.

79
00:08:00,200 --> 00:08:00,560
Old Yao.

80
00:08:00,880 --> 00:08:01,080
Mm?

81
00:08:02,040 --> 00:08:02,520
Come and look at this.

82
00:08:07,880 --> 00:08:08,240
Look at this.

83
00:08:09,320 --> 00:08:09,720
This is...

84
00:08:10,520 --> 00:08:11,160
We are getting closer...

85
00:08:12,360 --> 00:08:12,920
...closer and closer to him.

86
00:08:38,160 --> 00:08:40,640
This side looks like a woman.

87
00:08:41,200 --> 00:08:41,680
But what about this side?

88
00:08:44,560 --> 00:08:45,520
This drawing is not yet finished.

89
00:08:46,480 --> 00:08:47,240
He intends to kill again.

90
00:08:47,920 --> 00:08:48,840
Shentu is right.

91
00:08:49,440 --> 00:08:50,600
The killer took the internal organs.

92
00:08:51,360 --> 00:08:52,240
It was not done at random.

93
00:08:52,880 --> 00:08:53,720
Perhaps they serve a greater purpose.

94
00:08:54,800 --> 00:08:56,040
But three of the five organs are already taken.

95
00:08:56,560 --> 00:08:57,560
He certainly will not stop.

96
00:08:59,120 --> 00:09:00,640
What do you think he intends to do?

97
00:09:02,120 --> 00:09:02,560
Borrowing Life.

98
00:09:03,800 --> 00:09:04,240
Borrowing Life?

99
00:09:04,680 --> 00:09:04,960
Yes.

100
00:09:06,080 --> 00:09:07,600
Legend has it there is a dark art.

101
00:09:08,440 --> 00:09:09,600
Taking five healthy organs...

102
00:09:10,120 --> 00:09:11,240
...supplemented by a puppet...

103
00:09:12,040 --> 00:09:12,800
...and casting a spell...

104
00:09:15,400 --> 00:09:17,720
...can bring the dying back to life.

105
00:09:18,560 --> 00:09:19,040
A puppet.

106
00:09:19,480 --> 00:09:19,720
Yes.

107
00:09:22,360 --> 00:09:23,240
Do you remember last night...

108
00:09:23,680 --> 00:09:25,560
...what was found in Hong Ling's room?

109
00:09:28,280 --> 00:09:28,960
Wet sawdust.

110
00:09:35,440 --> 00:09:38,680
What do you think caused the drawing on the victim?

111
00:09:40,840 --> 00:09:41,360
Something like a carving knife.

112
00:09:42,800 --> 00:09:45,600
At first, I guessed the killer might be a carpenter.

113
00:09:46,480 --> 00:09:47,640
But you said a puppet is needed.

114
00:09:48,240 --> 00:09:49,080
Then he might be...

115
00:09:50,040 --> 00:09:50,840
...a Puppet Master.

116
00:09:53,440 --> 00:09:53,680
My Lord.

117
00:09:54,560 --> 00:09:54,960
Next...

118
00:09:55,640 --> 00:09:56,440
...what should we do?

119
00:09:57,040 --> 00:09:58,360
Based on the Madam's description last night...

120
00:09:59,000 --> 00:09:59,520
...redraw the portrait.

121
00:10:00,320 --> 00:10:01,320
Secretly investigate all of Chang'an's...

122
00:10:01,320 --> 00:10:02,160
...Puppet Masters.

123
00:10:02,880 --> 00:10:03,160
Take heed.

124
00:10:03,560 --> 00:10:04,680
You must not alert the enemy.

125
00:10:05,680 --> 00:10:05,880
Yes, sir.
